item.title: CVE-2024-37999|2024-07-08T10:29:56.906Z -- siemens -- medicalis%20workflow%20orchestrator
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Medicalis Workflow Orchestrator (All versions). The affected application executes as a trusted account with high privileges and network access. This could allow an authenticated local attacker to escalate privileges.
